        "TileImage": "$($repository 14ef9606-229b-4ee5-9f79-bd8fa7893e1e).Image",
        "Description": "Your primary target is Grengolis, now operating under the clever alias &quot;John Smith.&quot; He is currently posing as a pit crew mechanic. If you can lure him under his car, you might exact some poetic justice.\r\rLife has been unkind to Moon, now using the name &quot;Linsdey,&quot; and she can be found doing drugs in public restrooms. Do her a favor and choke her, preferably to death.\r\rFinally, Bo is as poor as ever and makes his money by selling counterfeit VIP passes. He now operates under the name &quot;Fishy Joe.&quot;",
